{
  "text": "Binary similarity has been recently subject to a lot of attention [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . This is due to its centrality in several tasks, such as discovery of known vulnerabilities in large collection of software, dispute on copyright matters, analysis and detection of malicious software, etc.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "6247943",
